  "decision_conditions": [
    "&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot; style=&quot;line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 12pt; margin-bottom: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;The proposed development, by reason of its siting and detailed design,&amp;nbsp; would represent an inappropriate form of development to the detriment of the character and appearance of the host building and the visual amenity of the surrounding area. As such the proposal is contrary to policy D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;D4 (Delivering good design) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;of the London Plan (2021) and policy LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) of the Hackney Local Plan 2020, and the relevant sections of the Residential Extensions and Alterations SPD (2009).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-3da64b8c-7fff-50bb-0ed9-7a0eb325b6af&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;",
    "<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; vertical-align: baseline;\">The proposed formation of the front terrace, by reason of its height and location would be likely to give rise to unacceptable levels of overlooking, or perceived overlooking and loss of privacy of neighbouring properties, to the detriment of the amenity of neighbouring occupiers. As such the proposal is contrary to policy D3 (Optimising site capacity through the design-led approach) of the London Plan (2021) and policies LP1 (Design Quality and Local Character) and LP2 (Development and Amenity) of the Hackney Local Plan (2020).</span></p><p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-40691d07-7fff-d1a5-4683-bfb8f57c10fb\"></span></p>"
  ],
